PROJECT NAME: Expense Tracker

INTRODUCTION:
Keeping track of your expenses is crucial to the financial stability of your personal or business budget.
To accurately and effectively examine all of your spending, you must maintain an accurate daily log of your assets and expenses.
What if you could use an application to do all of this work and just provide the data? 
This application will use concepts of python to create an expense tracker for daily to monthly expenses.

FEATURES;
- 1) Add Expense: User can add expenses by clicking 1, then input the amount and category of the expense 
- 2) View Total Expense: After inputting different expenses, users can see what the total expenses
- 3) View Expenses By Category: Users can input a category to see how much they have spent in that category only
- User Friendly Interface: Easy to use for anyone with easy interaction
